name: Coat of arms of CAU
description:
My gift for the first Ukrainian crypto art community.
The shield contains logotype of Ukrainian community, graphic visualization of blockchain, artists instruments and one of the hryvna's element - Sierpiński triangle. Last one was added to national currency by Heorhiy Narbut - one of the most important Ukrainian graphic designer of the twentieth century.

Proudly created By Odi Vandal 21 for Crypto Art Ukraine.
